== Media ==
=== Print ===
Lake Charles has many publications in circulation. The most-widely distributed, daily newspaper is ''[http://www.americanpress.com The American Press].'' Other popular periodicals include ''Lagniappe Magazine,''''[http://www.timessw.com The Times of Southwest Louisiana], Gumbo Magazine, and Thrive magazine; however, the latter three are non-daily.

===Television===
Major television network affiliates serving the area include:
* 7 [[KPLC]] ([[National Broadcasting Company|NBC]])
* 18 [[KLTL]] ([[Public Broadcasting System|PBS]])
* 29 [[KVHP]] ([[Fox Broadcasting Company|FOX]])

